    "answer_id" : 38168563,
    "question_id" : 1538755,
    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 3.0",
    "body" : "<p>Why not use a regular expression ?</p>\n\n<pre><code>public static boolean toBoolean( String target )\n{\n    if( target == null ) return false;\n    return target.matches( \"(?i:^(1|true|yes|oui|vrai|y)$)\" );\n}\n</code></pre>\n"
