    "question_id" : 1538755,
    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 4.0",
    "body" : "<p>We created <a href=\"https://github.com/thedocs-io/soyuz-to\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">soyuz-to</a> library to simplify this problem (convert X to Y). It's just a set of SO answers for similar questions. This might be strange to use the library for such a simple problem, but it really helps in a lot of similar cases.</p>\n\n<pre><code>import io.thedocs.soyuz.to;\n\nBoolean aBoolean = to.Boolean(\"true\");\n</code></pre>\n\n<p>Please check it - it's very simple and has a lot of other useful features</p>\n"
