    "body" : "<pre><code>boolean status=false;\nif (variable.equalsIgnoreCase(&quot;true&quot;)) {\n   status=true;  \n   }\n</code></pre>\n<p>This is supported only if the string is 'true' (not case-sensitive). Later you can play with the status variable.</p>\n"
